org.afplib.afplib

Interface MCF1RG

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Triplet
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MCF1RGImpl

    public interface MCF1RG
extends Triplet
    A representation of the model object 'MCF1RG'.

    The following features are supported:

    • CF Lid
    • Sectid
    • CF Name
    • CP Name
    • FCS Name
    • Char Rot

    See Also:
    AfplibPackage.getMCF1RG()
